title: Element Make It Count - Finland 2015
description:
Congrats to VILLE VIERIKKO who won the MAKE IT COUNT contest in Espoo, Finland !
Vege won a spot in the European Finals that will take place in Spain and a chance to win a trip to California to compete for Element sponsorship at Nyjah's park!

More info : elementmakeitcount.com

Special thanks to https://elmonstrino.bandcamp.com for the music!

under 13 :
1st – Albert Palola
2nd – Toni Lemtonen
3rd – Toivo Palomaa

14-16 : 
1st – Pekko Palomaa
2nd – Aaron Rautio
3rd – Vere Hongisto

17+ and Sponsored:
1st – Ville "Vege" Vierikko (overall winner)
2nd – Eric Jundqvist
3rd – Victo Palomaki
